assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6be4f2ac06e95a85107de36f42a38bc1c3e5f5","tid":777742,"uid":68892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97eb878dc6123c75bf06ac6c711cd22af76a7e44","tid":777742,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"備受內地人追捧的美心流心奶黃月餅券上月起兩度開售，結果全港各分店均引來不少市民排隊購買，當中更不乏炒家轉售圖利。距離中秋節還有個多月，西環一間30多年歷史的餅店推出「粗口月餅」，負責人於其Facebook專頁率先推出「X你咩哈哈」月餅，聲稱要為港人減壓，笑言：「到時你想送比老細 奶奶 新抱 高官 就隨便你喇」。<br />\n<br />\n位於西環的華爾登餅店自稱由1984年開店，至今已有30多年歷史，他們日前在其Facebook專頁推出「X你咩哈哈」月餅，隨即引來網民蜂擁訂購，昨日晚上他們再於專頁預告，未來將會推出一系列粗口月餅，「打七你 寶寶」「心好累 仆街」「好X正 呀喂」「X你咩 哈哈」「痴膠線 親親」及「係愛呀 哈利」月餅，未來將會公佈訂購詳情。<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇<br />\nJEssica Choi：要儲齊一套<br />\nLAM K K 快D整好post哂上來睇吓！<br />\nCherrie Cheung 可唔可以出隻一盒有晒6個款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534076899_a759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534076899_a759.jpg&h=2cbcf461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180813/58555290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58555290&d=%2FjI2VTkhbvnYLJGZcMNtS49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=314f10f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58555290&h=2cfdecb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180813/58555290</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"心好累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e94dc407cf8e2cfad6b92cbfd7946397081998","tid":777742,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08